<F P=100> Panama </F>
<H3> <TI>   Molirena Controversy Prompts Minister To Resign </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2601003794 Panama City Circuito RPC Television in Spanish 
2300 GMT 25 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2601003794 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City Circuito RPC Television </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "RPC Television News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Presidency Minister Julio Harris tendered his 
resignation to President Guillermo Endara today. In a letter to 
the president, Harris explained that his decision responds to 
the current political situation regarding the Nationalist 
Liberal Republican Movement [Molirena]. 

</TEXT>

