<F P=100> Panama </F>
<H3> <TI>   President Appoints Mayors in Several Municipalities </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2501204394 Panama City Telemetro Television Network in 
Spanish 1730 GMT 25 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2501204394 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City Telemetro Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Communique issued by the Presidency of the Republic in </F>
Panama City on 25 January; from the "Telemetro Reports" newscast] 
  [Text] His Excellency President Guillermo Endara Galimany, 
by virtue of the power vested in him, has appointed the 
following persons to occupy the mayoral posts in the following 
districts: Alcibiades Bustavino, mayor of Pese; Mario Melendez, 
mayor of Baru, Puerto Armuelles; Dora Lesbia Palacios, mayor of 
Anton; Enrique Batista, mayor of Rio de Jesus; Hector Ovidio 
Herrera, mayor of Atalaya; Nelson Martinez, mayor of Canazas; 
Adriano Moscoso, mayor of Santamaria; and Gabriela Pino Cosio, 
mayor of Calobre. 

</TEXT>

