Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Charallave, Venezuela, 26 Jan (AFP) -- High school 
and university students demonstrated today in this small city, 
50 km southeast of Caracas, marking the second consecutive day 
of street violence . 
  The students protested the death of a 16-year-old high 
school 
student, who was killed yesterday when a tear gas bomb hit her 
in the head. The incident took place amid disturbances in the 
bedroom community of Los Teques, 20 km southeast of Caracas. 

