<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] As part of his visit to Belgium, Ricardo Alarcon de 
Quesada, president of the National Assembly of the People's 
Government, today held work meetings with Belgian and European 
Parliament leaders. 
