meetings, the current situation and prospects for the Cuban 
economy were analyzed, as well as Cuba's relations with the 
European Union, how things might evolve, and fundamental 
projections of Cuban foreign policy. 
  Alarcon's visit to Brussels ends on 30 January following a 
campaign of solidarity with Cuba. 

