            Military    Police    Civilians    Subversives    Total 

Lima        0           1         1            0              2        20 

Northern    0           0         2            0              2        3 

Wari 

Central     0           0         0            24             24       5 

Jungle      6           0         8            0              14       8 

Total       6           1         11           24             42       36 



</TEXT>

