<F P=102>  BK3112130893 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1230 
GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> BK3112130893 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The prime minister has refused to accept the 
resignation of the finance minister, Dr. Manmohan Singh. This 
was stated by the official spokesman in New Delhi today. The 
prime minister, in a letter to Dr. Singh, said taking all 
factors into consideration, including the enormous agenda of 
work, it would not be appropriate for him to resign. 

</TEXT>

