<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A reliable security source has denied a report 
carried by some news media on an attempt to assassinate the 
president of the republic a month ago. This report is 
completely untrue, the source said, and called on all mass media 
not to publish such biased reports until they are verified by 
the competent security agencies. He also cautioned the citizens 
against believing such rumors, which seek to cast doubts on and 
shake confidence in the march to security and stability, which 
has gained strength over the past three years. 

